          <tr><td>Burner refurbish (full assembly)</td><td>$450–$780</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Main control board replacement</td><td>$650–$1,100</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Full fryer tube refurbish (LG line)</td><td>$800–$1,400</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p class="small">
        Most Vulcan fryer calls land $280–$650 parts-and-labor. LG500 large-capacity and VK125 jobs can run
        $600–$1,200 depending on failure complexity. Full cross-brand context in our <a href="/price-list/commercial-fryer-repair-cost/">commercial
        fryer repair cost guide</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
